{"word":"ἀδήλως","slug":"ἀδήλως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀδήλως</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄδηλος\">ἄδηλος</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> ‘not being clearly apparent’, <b><i>uncertainly</i></b> in imagery of Paul’s activity as a racer, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀδήλως\">ἀδήλως</a></el> <i>not aimlessly</i> = <i>with my eye on the goal</i> <b><a href='B:530 9:26'>1 Cor 9:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀδηλότης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀδημονέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}